bilingual.source: We need to expand the network coverage.
bilingual.target: 我们需要扩大网络的覆盖范围。

bilingual.source: This router has a wide signal coverage.
bilingual.target: 这个路由器的信号覆盖范围很广。

bilingual.source: The signal coverage of China Mobile is extensive.
bilingual.target: 中国移动的信号覆盖范围很广。

bilingual.source: The coverage of unicom is excellent in urban areas.
bilingual.target: 联通在城市地区的覆盖范围非常好。

bilingual.source: The coverage of the new mobile network is impressive.
bilingual.target: 新移动网络的覆盖范围令人印象深刻。

bilingual.source: The coverage of mobile communication networks is expanding.
bilingual.target: 移动通信网络的覆盖范围越来越广。

bilingual.source: The plan's coverage does not include international travel.
bilingual.target: 这个计划的覆盖范围不包括国际旅行。

bilingual.source: The book has a wide coverage, covering many topics.
bilingual.target: 这本书的覆盖范围非常广泛，涵盖了许多主题。

bilingual.source: The insurance coverage includes medical and dental expenses.
bilingual.target: 这份保险的覆盖范围包括医疗和牙科费用。

bilingual.source: The government is planning to expand Medicaid coverage next year.
bilingual.target: 政府计划明年扩大医疗补助的覆盖范围。

yingyinNormal.en: On average, they're paying just $82 a month for coverage.
yingyinNormal.zh: 平均下来,他们每月仅仅需要支付$82。

yingyinNormal.en: Global news coverage, celebrity visitors. Eyes of the world.
yingyinNormal.zh: 全球新闻头条，各界名流参观，世界瞩目。

yingyinNormal.en: What you're saying is if the coverage influences enough people...
yingyinNormal.zh: 你是说，如果新闻报道影响了足够多的人…

yingyinNormal.en: They found a plan with coverage they liked and it was way less expensive.
yingyinNormal.zh: 他们找到了一个他们想要的方案，这一方案不是那么贵。

yingyinNormal.en: So we may experience the odd drop in coverage during the first 24 hours...
yingyinNormal.zh: 所以开始使用的前24小时可能会出现覆盖率下降的故障…

yingyinNormal.en: Blanket coverage. Shove it in their faces. Show them that she is one of us now.
yingyinNormal.zh: 强迫式信息灌输，让人们看看她现在是我们这边的了。

yingyinNormal.en: What is it that you really want? I want Medicare coverage bumped up to where it was.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你到底想要什么？我想要医保覆盖率调回原来的水平。

yingyinNormal.en: Will the coverage extend to Jason? No, he's a freelancer. I don't think it's a problem.
yingyinNormal.zh: 能延伸支付杰森的保险吗？不行，他是自由职业者，我不知道还要考虑他。

yingyinNormal.en: Good afternoon, I'm Caesar Flickerman. Hear about continuing coverage of the defense of the Capitol.
yingyinNormal.zh: 下午好，我是凯萨·富莱克曼，请继续收看国会区保卫战消息的报道。

yingyinNormal.en: Blue Cross said my insurance was canceled. The severance package gave me health coverage for up to a year.
yingyinNormal.zh: 蓝十字会告诉我，保险被取消了。解雇金条款里规定了一年的健康保险。

yingyinNormal.en: Over the past ten years, the two of you combined have gotten less coverage than the average junior congressman from Nebraska.
yingyinNormal.zh: 在过去的十年中，关于你们夫妇的报道加起来还不到内布拉斯加州资浅众议员的平均水平。

yingyinNormal.en: More than seven million people enrolled in affordable coverage by visiting HealthCare.gov or going to the marketplace in their state.
yingyinNormal.zh: 700多万人通过访问HealthCare.gov，或者到他们自己州的市场上获得了平价医疗的覆盖。

yingyinNormal.en: No, no. We make it so that Cathy wins. We'll just make it look like the party chose her. And think of the coverage. We'll own the news.
yingyinNormal.zh: 不不，我们要想办法让凯茜获胜，只是要做得像是党选择了她，想想新闻报道吧，会铺天盖地的。

yingyinNormal.en: Yeah, and it's the kind of coverage that we can't really control. You know, I mean, these things have a way of taking on a life of their own.
yingyinNormal.zh: 而这种新闻我们也没办法控制，我是说这种风声会自己落地生根。

yingyinNormal.en: Insurance companies can no longer deny you coverage just because you have a preexisting condition and they now have to cover free preventive care like checkups and mammograms.
yingyinNormal.zh: 保险公司再也不能因为你已有健康问题而拒绝你，现在他们要对像体检和乳房X光检查这样的预防保健项目进行免费覆盖。

examination_example.sentence: Bills to expand Medicare <highlight>coverage</highlight> of telemedicine have bipartisan (两党的) support in Congress.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 扩大医疗保险对远程医疗覆盖的法案在国会得到两党的支持。

examination_example.sentence: Insurance <highlight>coverage</highlight> varies from health plan to health plan, and a big federal plan covers only a narrow range of services.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 保险覆盖范围因健康计划而异，一个大的联邦计划只覆盖很小的服务范围。

examination_example.sentence: The move was a switch to leverage on the <highlight>coverage</highlight> of their fashion week show to make stock available immediately to consumers.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 这一举措是为了利用时装周的报道，让消费者可以立即买到商品。

examination_example.sentence: In a recent month of TV news <highlight>coverage</highlight> of American youth, just 2% of teens were shown at home.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 在最近一个月关于美国青少年的电视新闻报道中，只有2%的青少年在家中出现。
